Sun May 25 04:11:37 UTC 2008  Ken Sedgwick  <ken+5a4@bonsai.com>

        * rpmbuild/ace-tao.spec:
        * rpmbuild/ace-tao-rnq.patch:
        * rpmbuild/ace-tao-config-tmplvis.patch:
        * rpmbuild/ace-tao-hasicmp.patch:
